examples.en: It can't be helped.
I helped to milk the cows.
He helped me out, again.
He helped her do the dishes.
They helped to cook the meal.
I helped in my own small way.
Kudos to everyone who helped.
The cold helped clear his head.
He cheered her, and that helped.
She helped to move the furniture.
Drugs helped to relieve the pain.
She helped herself to the dessert.
We helped them in / with their work.
He helped me to unfreeze my computer.
A nice lady at the library helped me.
Residents have helped us plant trees.
She helped him choose some new clothes.
They helped her out of a sense of duty.
She helped the old man across the road.
The medicine helped calm her breathing.
Reading helped to expand her vocabulary.
She helped him fight his drug addiction.
He helped pioneer a new route to the West.
Why haven't you ever helped me before now?
They helped their party retake the Senate.
I want to thank everyone who helped today.
Everyone helped out during the earthquake.
She had never helped with any of the bills.
The pile of leaves helped cushion his fall.
Your support helped the team on to victory.
